"{\"uid\": \"timesofindia.indiatimes.com-india-pm-modi-mann-ki-baat-live-updates-olympics-2024-union-budget-akashvani-liveblog-112074375.cms\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"'Mann Ki Baat': PM Modi praises Project Pari for beautifying public spaces  In the 112th episode of 'Mann Ki Baat', Prime Minister Narendra Modi said, \\\"A country can progress only by taking pride in its culture.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 131, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many such efforts are being made in India, one of which is Project Pari.\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8365799260609777e-14, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You might have noticed the beautiful paintings on roadside walls and in underpasses.\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These artworks are created by artists associated with Project Pari.\\\"\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mann ki Baat Live: Khadi sales surge by 400%, PM says  The turnover of Khadi Village Industries has surpassed Rs 1.5 lakh crore for the first time, with Khadi sales increasing by 400%.\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man\", \"score\": 0.9950686637751104, \"rank\": 0.0049541240462798505, \"text\": \"Mann\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man\"}, {\"begin\": 448, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAAT\", \"score\": 0.9999999035335396, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Baat\", \"types\": [\"Q7187\", \"Q206229\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAAT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAAT\"}, {\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khadi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Khadi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khadi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khadi\"}, {\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khadi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Khadi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khadi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khadi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This surge in sales is also generating numerous new employment opportunities.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As most of the workers in this industry are women, they are the ones reaping the maximum benefits.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PM Modi introduces 'Manas', new helpline for drug rehabilitation  The government has opened a special center named 'Manas', making it a major step in the fight against drugs.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manas_National_Park\", \"score\": 0.999995680526133, \"rank\": 3.0082250489558742e-06, \"text\": \"Manas\", \"types\": [\"Q473972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manas_National_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manas_National_Park\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recently, the helpline and portal for 'Manas' were launched.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The government has also issued a toll-free number, '1933'.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone can call this number to receive necessary advice or information related to rehabilitation, says PM Modi.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1201, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1145506917199964e-20, \"text\": \"PM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_India\"}, {\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.662473317782822e-46, \"text\": \"Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mann ki Baat Live: PM Modi on Unnati self help group  \\\"Let us talk about colours-colours that have brought prosperity to the lives of over 250 women in Rohtak district, Haryana.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak_district\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rohtak district\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak_district\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak_district\"}, {\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1544492236629883e-12, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These women, who are part of the handloom industry, previously managed small shops and did minor work to make ends meet.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, driven by the desire to progress, they decided to join the Unnati Self-Help Group.\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Through this group, they received training in block printing and dyeing, transforming their lives,\\\" said PM Modi  PM Modi invites tourists to India's newest world heritage site  In the 112th episode of 'Mann Ki Baat', Prime Minister Narendra Modi said, \\\"With Charaideo Maidam now a World Heritage Site, it will attract more tourism.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8365799260609777e-14, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 1861, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charaideo\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.5933247391749586e-12, \"text\": \"Charaideo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charaideo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charaideo\"}, {\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maidam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I encourage you to include this site in your future travel plans.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On March 9 of this year, I had the honor of unveiling the tallest statue of the great Ahom warrior Lachit Borphukan.\\\"\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2100, \"end\": 2116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lachit_Borphukan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lachit Borphukan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lachit_Borphukan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lachit_Borphukan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Project Pari: PM Modi urges greater focus on public art in India  A country can progress only by taking pride in its culture.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8365799260609777e-14, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many such efforts are being made in India, one of which is Project Pari, meaning Public Art of India.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2282, \"end\": 2287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8365799260609777e-14, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, at Bharat Mandapam in Delhi, you can see incredible artworks from across the nation.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2364, \"end\": 2370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5879062370418704e-20, \"text\": \"Bharat\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 2371, \"end\": 2379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandapam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3613063393698762e-18, \"text\": \"Mandapam\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandapam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandapam\"}, {\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.99948840850848, \"rank\": 0.0005118533514759235, \"text\": \"Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I urge art and culture enthusiasts to contribute more to public art initiatives.\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mann ki Baat Live: PM Modi celebrates India's top 5 finish at International Mathematics Olympiad  In the 112th episode of 'Mann Ki Baat', Prime Minister Narendra Modi said, \\\"Recently, the world witnessed the Olympics of mathematics - the International Mathematics Olympiad.\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2566, \"end\": 2571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8365799260609777e-14, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 2590, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Mathematical_Olympiad\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Mathematics Olympiad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Mathematical_Olympiad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Mathematical_Olympiad\"}, {\"begin\": 2681, \"end\": 2694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Mathematical_Olympiad\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Mathematics Olympiad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Mathematical_Olympiad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Mathematical_Olympiad\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Youth from over 100 countries participated, and our team achieved remarkable success, securing a spot in the top five overall.\\\"\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Cheer for Bharat': PM Modi urges nation to support and encourage Paris Olympics athletes  In the 112th episode of 'Mann Ki Baat', Prime Minister Narendra Modi says \\\"In the entire world, Paris Olympic is all over there at this point of time.\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 3172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3077, \"end\": 3090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 3118, \"end\": 3123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999959073, \"rank\": 3.972066569823678e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our players have the opportunity to let our tricolour at the world level, they have this opportunity to do something for the country.\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You all should encourage them.\\\"\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mann ki Baat Live: PM on Assam's Charaideo Maidams  In the 112th episode of 'Mann Ki Baat', Prime Minister Narendra Modi announced, \\\"Charaideo Maidam of Assam is being included in the Unesco World Heritage Sites.\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3447, \"end\": 3460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 3473, \"end\": 3482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charaideo\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.5933247391749586e-12, \"text\": \"Charaideo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charaideo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charaideo\"}, {\"begin\": 3483, \"end\": 3489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maidam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidam\"}, {\"begin\": 3524, \"end\": 3551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Heritage_Site\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Unesco World Heritage Sites\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Heritage_Site\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Heritage_Site\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be India's 43rd site on the list and the first from the Northeast.\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3566, \"end\": 3571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8365799260609777e-14, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Charaideo, meaning 'a shining city on the hills,' was the first capital of the Ahom dynasty.\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Traditionally, the people of the Ahom dynasty preserved the mortal remains of their ancestors and their valuables in the Moidams.\\\"\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PM Modi Mann ki Baat Live: 'Cheer for Bharat'  \\\"At this moment, the Paris Olympics is capturing global attention.\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics offer our athletes a chance to proudly wave the tricolor on the world stage and achieve something remarkable for our country.\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 4107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I urge you to support our athletes and Cheer for Bharat!\\\"\", \"from\": 4108, \"to\": 4165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4157, \"end\": 4163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5879062370418704e-20, \"text\": \"Bharat\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"he said.\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mann ki Baat Live: Prime Minister Narendra Modi interacts with International Mathematics Olympiad champs  A six-member team of Indian students represented India at the 2024 International Mathematics Olympiad, held in Bath, United Kingdom, from July 11 to July 22.\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4176, \"end\": 4180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man\", \"score\": 0.9950686637751104, \"rank\": 0.0049541240462798505, \"text\": \"Mann\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man\"}, {\"begin\": 4184, \"end\": 4188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAAT\", \"score\": 0.9999999035335396, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Baat\", \"types\": [\"Q7187\", \"Q206229\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAAT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAAT\"}, {\"begin\": 4210, \"end\": 4223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 4239, \"end\": 4273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Mathematical_Olympiad\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Mathematics Olympiad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Mathematical_Olympiad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Mathematical_Olympiad\"}, {\"begin\": 4303, \"end\": 4309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.999811275362036, \"rank\": 0.00018876024728635047, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 4331, \"end\": 4336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8365799260609777e-14, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 4393, \"end\": 4397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bath_Rugby\", \"score\": 0.9930120846119908, \"rank\": 0.007037089977332814, \"text\": \"Bath\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bath_Rugby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bath_Rugby\"}, {\"begin\": 4399, \"end\": 4413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999961490517788, \"rank\": 2.9096172809094835e-06, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team achieved remarkable success, winning four gold medals and one silver.\", \"from\": 4440, \"to\": 4518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prime Minister Narendra Modi congratulated the team, calling the achievement \\\"a matter of immense joy and pride.\\\"\", \"from\": 4519, \"to\": 4632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4534, \"end\": 4547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Mo